OL,3,CWhat do we know about the Ebola
OL,4,Coutbreak and what is the risk to the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FThe Ebola outbreak in the Democratic
OL,8,FRepublic of Congo and Uganda, which
OL,9,Fhas left at least 88 people dead, was
OL,10,Fdeclared a public health emergency by
OL,11,Fthe World Health Organization on
OL,12,FSunday.
OL,14,FEbola is a highly contagious virus
OL,15,Fthat can be contracted via bodily
OL,16,Ffluids such as vomit, blood or semen.
OL,17,FThe disease it causes is rare, but can
OL,18,Fbe severe and often fatal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
