OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779109902
OL,3,CWhat do we know about the Ebola
OL,4,Coutbreak and what is the risk to the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FIn a post on X, the World Health
OL,8,FOrganisation (WHO) said the outbreak
OL,9,Fdoes not meet the criteria of a
OL,10,Fpandemic emergency, like Covid-19, and
OL,11,Fadvised against the closure of
OL,12,Finternational borders.
OL,14,FITV News explains what you need to
OL,15,Fknow about the Ebola outbreak so far.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
