OL,3,CWhat do we know about the Ebola
OL,4,Coutbreak and what is the risk to the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FDr Anne Cori, Associate Professor in
OL,8,FInfectious Disease Modelling at
OL,9,FImperial College London, said: "There
OL,10,Fis limited scientific evidence on this
OL,11,FEbola species as there are only two
OL,12,Fhistorical outbreaks recorded. These
OL,13,Fpoint to a highly lethal disease with
OL,14,Fan estimated 1 in 3 cases dying."
OL,16,FWhat are the symptoms?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
