OL,3,CWhat do we know about the Ebola
OL,4,Coutbreak and what is the risk to the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FWHO said the outbreak is impacting the
OL,8,FDRC's remote northeastern Ituri
OL,9,Fprovince on the border with Uganda.
OL,11,FCases have also appeared in the
OL,12,FCongolese capital, Kinshasa, and in
OL,13,Fthe city of Goma.
OL,15,FThe US Centres for Disease Control and
OL,16,FPrevention (CDC) has reported at least
OL,17,F10 confirmed cases, and at least 336
OL,18,Fsuspected cases, including 88 deaths
OL,19,Fin the DRC.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
