OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779109902
OL,3,CWhat do we know about the Ebola
OL,4,Coutbreak and what is the risk to the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FTwo laboratory-confirmed cases have
OL,8,Fnow been reported in Uganda, including
OL,9,Fone death. The two cases had no
OL,10,Fapparent link to each other, but the
OL,11,Findividuals had travelled from the DRC.
OL,13,FThe Congolese health minister has
OL,14,Fannounced the opening of three
OL,15,Ftreatment centers in eastern Congo.
OL,17,FWhy are experts worried?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
