OL,3,CWhat do we know about the Ebola
OL,4,Coutbreak and what is the risk to the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FWHO previously declared a PHEIC during
OL,8,Fthe large Ebola outbreak in North Kivu
OL,9,Fand Ituri provinces in DRC between
OL,10,F2018 and 2020, and before that during
OL,11,Fthe 2014`2016 West Africa Ebola
OL,12,Fepidemic.
OL,14,FWhat's being done to contain the
OL,15,Foutbreak?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
