OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779109902
OL,3,CWhat do we know about the Ebola
OL,4,Coutbreak and what is the risk to the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FThe CDC said Sunday that it is
OL,8,Fdeploying resources from its offices
OL,9,Fin Uganda and the DRC to help with
OL,10,Fefforts, including surveillance,
OL,11,Fcontact tracing, and laboratory
OL,12,Ftesting.
OL,14,FThe CDC will also mobilise additional
OL,15,Fsupport from the agency's headquarters
OL,16,Fin Atlanta, Georgia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779109902
OL,3,CWhat do we know about the Ebola
OL,4,Coutbreak and what is the risk to the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FDr. Satish Pillai, a deputy director
OL,8,Fin the Division of Preparedness and
OL,9,FEmerging Infections, said that the CDC
OL,10,Fwas unaware of any exposure on
OL,11,Finternational flights and noted that
OL,12,Fboth the DRC and Uganda have exit
OL,13,Fscreening measures in place to prevent
OL,14,Fthe spread of the virus through travel.
OL,16,FWhat is the risk to the UK?
OL,18,FIt is not considered that this
OL,19,Foutbreak has a risk of spreading
OL,20,Fglobally - and that's why it hasn't
OL,21,Fbeen deemed a global pandemic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
