OL,3,CWhat do we know about the Ebola
OL,4,Coutbreak and what is the risk to the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FSince 1976, there have only been four
OL,8,Fconfirmed reported in the UK.
OL,10,FOne was a laboratory-acquired case in
OL,11,F1976 and 3 cases were in healthcare
OL,12,Fworkers associated with the West
OL,13,FAfrican epidemic 2014 to 2015.
OL,15,FThere has never been an Ebola-related
OL,16,Fdeath in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
